          <h2>Slack Live Chat</h2>
          <p>
            Chatbots are of course very smart, and have an answer for almost
            everything. But there are also situations where a chatbot should
            better hand over the conversation to a real person. We at Apptiva
            mostly use slack channels for live chats. Therefore it was obvious
            to integrate Slack in a simple way with Bubble CMS.
          </p>
          <p>
            When creating an intent, the user can now select a so-called "Slack
            Expert Intent". When this intent is triggered, the chatbot will
            start a conversation with the previously configured slack channel.
          </p>
