        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <div class="item-description">
          <h2>Markdown</h2>
          <p>
            Text-based responses are great. But sometimes it's good if you can
            integrate a link in an answer, or maybe even display an image. For
            this reason we have integrated the use of Markdown in answer
            bubbles. In addition to images and links, the answers can be
            formatted as desired.
          </p>
